### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### Create speciality
POST http://localhost:8080/api/specialite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "CS",
  "libelle": "Computer Science"
}

### Get all specialities
GET http://localhost:8080/api/specialite

### Create professor
POST http://localhost:8080/api/professeur
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "Smith",
  "prenom": "John",
  "telephone": "+1-555-1000",
  "email": "john.smith@example.com",
  "dateEmbauche": "2024-01-15",
  "specialite": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

### Get all professors
GET http://localhost:8080/api/professeur

### Get professors by speciality
GET http://localhost:8080/api/professeur/specialite/1

### Filter professors by hiring date
GET http://localhost:8080/api/professeur/filterByDate?dateDebut=2024-01-01&dateFin=2024-12-31
